    <h1>Grievance Redressal Policy</h1>

    <p>
        Kalash is committed to providing a transparent, fair, and responsive grievance redressal mechanism
        in accordance with applicable Indian laws and regulations.
    </p>

    <p>
        Users who have any complaints, concerns, or grievances relating to the Kalash platform, its services,
        content, or operations may raise such grievances in the manner described below.
    </p>

    <ul>
        <li>All grievances should be submitted in writing via email to the designated Grievance Officer.</li>
        <li>Kalash shall acknowledge receipt of the grievance within 48 (forty-eight) hours.</li>
        <li>Kalash shall make reasonable efforts to resolve the grievance within 15 (fifteen) business days.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="contact">
        <strong>Grievance Officer Details:</strong><br>
        Name: Compliance Officer<br>
        Email: grievance@kalash.app<br>
        Working Hours: Monday to Friday, 10:00 AM â€“ 6:00 PM IST
    </div>

    <p>
        If a user is not satisfied with the resolution provided, the user may pursue remedies available under
        applicable Indian law.
    </p>

